thread.title: Wynn Resorts Announces First Quarter Earnings Release Date

author: cnbc.com
title: Wynn Resorts Announces First Quarter Earnings Release Date
text:
LAS VEGAS--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- Wynn Resorts, Limited (NASDAQ: WYNN) announced today that it will release the Company’s financial results for the first 2018 after the market close on Tuesday, April 24, 2018, followed by a conference call at 1:30 p.m. PT (4:30 p.m. ET).
The call will be broadcast live at www.wynnresorts.com under the “Company Information” section. Interested parties may also dial (800) 857-5022 or, for international callers, (415) 228-5000. The conference call ID is 9694971.
A replay of the call will be available through May 25, 2018 by dialing (888) 562-4492 or, for international callers, (402) 530-7666. The replay access code is 9694971. The call will also be archived at www.wynnresorts.com .
View source version on businesswire.com : https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180419006427/en/
